# MYCA Worldview Cross-System Integration (All Agents)

## When This Rule Applies

**When working on anything that touches** MYCA AI, MAS, Search, Memory, Consciousness, Brain, MINDEX, MycoBrain, Services, Protocols, Apps, NatureOS, NLM, Data, or Training modules—**check integration points** and ensure systems work together.

## Systems and Touch Points

| System | Key Paths | Integration Points |
|--------|-----------|--------------------|
| **MAS** | `mycosoft_mas/core/`, routers | All API routes, agent registry, orchestrator |
| **NLM** | `mycosoft_mas/nlm/`, NLM repo | Translation, NMF, bio-tokens, nlm_api router, NLMSensor |
| **Consciousness** | `consciousness/world_model.py`, sensors | WorldState, CREP, Earth2, NLM, EarthLIVE, MINDEX, MycoBrain, Presence |
| **MINDEX** | mindex repo, mindex_router | Unified search, species, compounds, NLM query_knowledge_graph |
| **Memory** | `memory/`, memory_api | Context injection, storage, recall |
| **Search** | Website Fluid Search, MINDEX | Unified search API, compound/species widgets |
| **MycoBrain** | localhost:8003, MycoBrainSensor | device_telemetry, heartbeats |
| **NatureOS** | Mycorrhizae, NatureOSSensor | ecosystem_status, channels |
| **EarthLIVE** | `earthlive/`, EarthLIVESensor | Weather, seismic, satellite → WorldState.earthlive_packet |
| **Protocols** | MDP, MMP, HPL, FCI (Mycorrhizae) | Envelopes, semantic translator |
| **Training** | `nlm/training`, `nlm/inference` | NLMTrainer, telemetry ingest |

## Mandatory Checks

1. **Before changing a sensor** – Confirm WorldState fields and `update_all`/`_update_*` handlers.
2. **Before changing NLM** – Confirm nlm_api router, NLM client, NLMSensor, MINDEX query path.
3. **Before changing APIs** – Update `docs/API_CATALOG_FEB04_2026.md` and `docs/SYSTEM_REGISTRY_FEB04_2026.md`.
4. **Before changing World Model** – Confirm all sensors, `to_summary()`, and downstream consumers.

